1/frozen-margaritas-ingredients-best.jpg 1333w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/frozen-margaritas-ingredients-best-200x300.jpg 200w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/frozen-margaritas-ingredients-best-683x1024.jpg 683w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/frozen-margaritas-ingredients-best-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/frozen-margaritas-ingredients-best-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/frozen-margaritas-ingredients-best-67x100.jpg 67w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/frozen-margaritas-ingredients-best-40x60.jpg 40w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/frozen-margaritas-ingredients-best-750x1125.jpg 750w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/frozen-margaritas-ingredients-best-730x1095.jpg 730w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/frozen-margaritas-ingredients-best-700x1050.jpg 700w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/frozen-margaritas-ingredients-best-550x825.jpg 550w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/frozen-margaritas-ingredients-best-156x234.jpg 156w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 1200px) 730px, (min-width: 1080px) 650px, (min-width: 1024px) 630px, calc(100vw - 40px)\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%201333%202000\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/frozen-margaritas-ingredients-best.jpg 1333w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/frozen-margaritas-ingredients-best-200x300.jpg 200w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/frozen-margaritas-ingredients-best-683x1024.jpg 683w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/frozen-margaritas-ingredients-best-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/frozen-margaritas-ingredients-best-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/frozen-margaritas-ingredients-best-67x100.jpg 67w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/frozen-margaritas-ingredients-best-40x60.jpg 40w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/frozen-margaritas-ingredients-best-750x1125.jpg 750w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/frozen-margaritas-ingredients-best-730x1095.jpg 730w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/frozen-margaritas-ingredients-best-700x1050.jpg 700w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/frozen-margaritas-ingredients-best-550x825.jpg 550w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/frozen-margaritas-ingredients-best-156x234.jpg 156w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/frozen-margaritas-ingredients-best.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003ch2 id=\"h-ingredients-for-a-frozen-margarita\"\u003eIngredients for a frozen margarita: \u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eTequila:\u003c/strong\u003e Choose your favorite to suit your own budget and tequila tastes!\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eLime juice:\u003c/strong\u003e You can use the bottled lime juice in a pinch, but try and squeeze fresh limes if possible for the brightest tart flavor.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eTriple sec:\u003c/strong\u003e Triple sec brings a sweetness and a layer of citrus orange flavor to your margarita. You can also use Cointreau (or Grand Marnier) which is more expensive and lighter on the sugar or fresh orange juice if you want natural sweetness.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eAgave nectar:\u003c/strong\u003e Using \u003ca href=\"https://amzn.to/4fMVRK1\"\u003elight agave syrup \u003c/a\u003eprovides a natural sweetener for your skinny margarita rather than using the classic simple syrup (it’s similar to honey).\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIce:\u003c/strong\u003e Adding crushed ice cubes will give you the slushy consistency that you’ve been dreaming of! You can also sub in some frozen fruit for an additional flavor.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eFor your glassware, you can use either the \u003ca href=\"https://amzn.to/3CAwfSg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\"\u003eclassic margarita glasses\u003c/a\u003e or more of a \u003ca href=\"https://amzn.to/4fpYFNB\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\"\u003eshorter tumbler\u003c/a\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cblockquote\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eTIP:\u003c/strong\u003e You can make your frozen margaritas a few hours ahead of time and store the mixture in the freezer until ready to serve.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/blockquote\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" width=\"1333\" height=\"2000\" data-pin-url=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/frozen-margarita-recipe/?tp_image_id=134412\" data-pin-title=\"the best frozen margarita\" src=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/frozen-margaritas-best-salt-rim.jpg\" alt=\"frozen margarita salt rim\" srcset=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/frozen-margaritas-best-salt-rim.jpg 1333w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/frozen-margaritas-best-salt-rim-200x300.jpg 200w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/frozen-margaritas-best-salt-rim-683x1024.jpg 683w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/frozen-margaritas-best-salt-rim-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/frozen-margaritas-best-salt-rim-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/frozen-margaritas-best-salt-rim-67x100.jpg 67w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/frozen-margaritas-best-salt-rim-40x60.jpg 40w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/frozen-margaritas-best-salt-rim-750x1125.jpg 750w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/frozen-margaritas-best-salt-rim-730x1095.jpg 730w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/frozen-margaritas-best-salt-rim-700x1050.jpg 700w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/frozen-margaritas-best-salt-rim-550x825.jpg 550w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/frozen-margaritas-best-salt-rim-156x234.jpg 156w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 1200px) 730px, (min-width: 1080px) 650px, (min-width: 1024px) 630px, calc(100vw - 40px)\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%201333%202000\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/frozen-margaritas-best-salt-rim.jpg 1333w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/frozen-margaritas-best-salt-rim-200x300.jpg 200w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/frozen-margaritas-best-salt-rim-683x1024.jpg 683w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/frozen-margaritas-best-salt-rim-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/frozen-margaritas-best-salt-rim-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/frozen-margaritas-best-salt-rim-67x100.jpg 67w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/frozen-margaritas-best-salt-rim-40x60.jpg 40w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/frozen-margaritas-best-salt-rim-750x1125.jpg 750w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/frozen-margaritas-best-salt-rim-730x1095.jpg 730w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/frozen-margaritas-best-salt-rim-700x1050.jpg 700w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/frozen-margaritas-best-salt-rim-550x825.jpg 550w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/frozen-margaritas-best-salt-rim-156x234.jpg 156w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/frozen-margaritas-best-salt-rim.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003ch3 id=\"h-how-to-make-a-salt-rim\"\u003eHow to make a salt rim:\u003c/h3\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eWhile you can use lime juice to adhere your salt to the rim of your glass, agave is a little more hearty and holds more salt than lime juice alone. When you do a salt rim, be sure to only do the outside edge so unwanted salt isn’t falling into your drink.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eTo make a salt-rimmed glass, add your agave to a small plate and roll the rim of the glass into the sticky substance (or run a wedge of lime around the top of the glass if using a lime). Next, dip the sticky rim onto a plate with a layer of either \u003ca href=\"https://amzn.to/3RrkLpP\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"\u003emargarita salt\u003c/a\u003e, course kosher salt, or course sea salt so the salt sticks to the tacky surface (try zesting a lime or orange peel into your salt as well for an extra zing). You can always salt just half the glass rim so that way guests can use either side depending on whether or not they enjoy a salted rim.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eThere are a few simple bar tools that will make your homemade frozen margarita experience simpler and quicker. I recommend \u003ca href=\"https://amzn.to/46iOvJr\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"\u003ea handheld citrus squeezer\u003c/a\u003e, a \u003ca href=\"https://amzn.to/3tbQTmY\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"\u003emeasuring shot glass\u003c/a\u003e and \u003ca href=\"https://amzn.to/48VvIXh\"\u003ecountertop blender\u003c/a\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" width=\"683\" height=\"1024\" data-pin-url=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/frozen-margarita-recipe/?tp_image_id=134411\" data-id=\"134411\" data-pin-title=\"the best froze