as-best-1-6-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/frozen-margaritas-best-1-6.jpg 1333w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/frozen-margaritas-best-1-6-67x100.jpg 67w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/frozen-margaritas-best-1-6-40x60.jpg 40w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/frozen-margaritas-best-1-6-750x1125.jpg 750w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/frozen-margaritas-best-1-6-730x1095.jpg 730w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/frozen-margaritas-best-1-6-700x1050.jpg 700w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/frozen-margaritas-best-1-6-550x825.jpg 550w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/frozen-margaritas-best-1-6-156x234.jpg 156w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/frozen-margaritas-best-1-6-683x1024.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" width=\"683\" height=\"1024\" data-pin-url=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/frozen-margarita-recipe/?tp_image_id=134410\" data-id=\"134410\" data-pin-title=\"the best frozen margarita\" src=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/frozen-margaritas-best-1-5-683x1024.jpg\" alt=\"making frozen margaritas\" srcset=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/frozen-margaritas-best-1-5-683x1024.jpg 683w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/frozen-margaritas-best-1-5-200x300.jpg 200w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/frozen-margaritas-best-1-5-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/frozen-margaritas-best-1-5-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/frozen-margaritas-best-1-5.jpg 1333w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/frozen-margaritas-best-1-5-67x100.jpg 67w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/frozen-margaritas-best-1-5-40x60.jpg 40w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/frozen-margaritas-best-1-5-750x1125.jpg 750w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/frozen-margaritas-best-1-5-730x1095.jpg 730w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/frozen-margaritas-best-1-5-700x1050.jpg 700w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/frozen-margaritas-best-1-5-550x825.jpg 550w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/frozen-margaritas-best-1-5-156x234.jpg 156w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 1200px) 730px, (min-width: 1080px) 650px, (min-width: 1024px) 630px, calc(100vw - 40px)\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%20683%201024\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/frozen-margaritas-best-1-5-683x1024.jpg 683w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/frozen-margaritas-best-1-5-200x300.jpg 200w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/frozen-margaritas-best-1-5-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/frozen-margaritas-best-1-5-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/frozen-margaritas-best-1-5.jpg 1333w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/frozen-margaritas-best-1-5-67x100.jpg 67w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/frozen-margaritas-best-1-5-40x60.jpg 40w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/frozen-margaritas-best-1-5-750x1125.jpg 750w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/frozen-margaritas-best-1-5-730x1095.jpg 730w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/frozen-margaritas-best-1-5-700x1050.jpg 700w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/frozen-margaritas-best-1-5-550x825.jpg 550w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/frozen-margaritas-best-1-5-156x234.jpg 156w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/frozen-margaritas-best-1-5-683x1024.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003ch2 id=\"h-instructions-for-making-a-frozen-margarita\"\u003eInstructions for making a frozen margarita:\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eAdd\u003c/strong\u003e your ingredients to a countertop blender.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eBlend\u003c/strong\u003e until smooth.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003ePour\u003c/strong\u003e into \u003ca href=\"https://amzn.to/3YJZQ3f\"\u003emargarita glasses\u003c/a\u003e (optionally rimmed with salt) and garnish with a lime wedge.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cem\u003eTIP:\u003c/em\u003e If your drink looks too “loose” and not slushy enough, add a little more ice and blend again until desired thickness is achieved. If it ever gets too thick to drink or pour, add a little more of each liquid ingredient and blend again.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" width=\"1333\" height=\"2000\" data-pin-url=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/frozen-margarita-recipe/?tp_image_id=134406\" data-pin-title=\"the best frozen margarita\" src=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/frozen-margaritas-best-1-1.jpg\" alt=\"frozen margarita\" srcset=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/frozen-margaritas-best-1-1.jpg 1333w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/frozen-margaritas-best-1-1-200x300.jpg 200w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/frozen-margaritas-best-1-1-683x1024.jpg 683w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/frozen-margaritas-best-1-1-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/frozen-margaritas-best-1-1-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/frozen-margaritas-best-1-1-67x100.jpg 67w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/frozen-margaritas-best-1-1-40x60.jpg 40w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/frozen-margaritas-best-1-1-750x1125.jpg 750w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/frozen-margaritas-best-1-1-730x1095.jpg 730w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/frozen-margaritas-best-1-1-700x1050.jpg 700w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/frozen-margaritas-best-1-1-550x825.jpg 550w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/frozen-margaritas-best-1-1-156x234.jpg 156w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 1200px) 730px, (min-width: 1080px) 650px, (min-width: 1024px) 630px, calc(100vw - 40px)\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%201333%202000\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/frozen-margaritas-best-1-1.jpg 1333w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/frozen-margaritas-best-1-1-200x300.jpg 200w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/frozen-margaritas-best-1-1-683x1024.jpg 683w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/frozen-margaritas-best-1-1-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/frozen-margaritas-best-1-1-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/frozen-margaritas-best-1-1-67x100.jpg 67w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/frozen-margaritas-best-1-1-40x60.jpg 40w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/frozen-margaritas-best-1-1-750x1125.jpg 750w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/frozen-margaritas-best-1-1-730x1095.jpg 730w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/frozen-margaritas-best-1-1-700x1050.jpg 700w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/frozen-margaritas-best-1-1-550x825.jpg 550w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/frozen-margaritas-best-1-1-156x234.jpg 156w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/frozen-margaritas-best-1-1.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003ch2 id=\"h-variations-on-a-frozen-margarita\"\u003eVariations on a frozen margarita:\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eLimeade frozen margarita\u003c/strong\u003e: In place of the fresh lime juice, try a can of frozen limeade concentrate instead!\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eStrawberry frozen margarita:\u003c/strong\u003e Sub out half the ice for frozen strawberries to make a berry flavored treat.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eMango frozen margarita:\u003c/strong\u003e Try our \u003ca href=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/frozen-mango-margaritas/\"\u003efrozen mango recipe\u003c/a\u003e for a tropical variation on the classic.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHibiscus frozen margarita:\u003c/strong\u003e This \u003ca href=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/frozen-hibiscus-margarita/\"\u003edelicious cocktai\u003c/a\u003el uses homemade hibiscus syrup for a unique flavor and a vibrant color.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eAvocado frozen margarita:\u003c/strong\u003e For a creamier margarita, \u003ca href=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/frozen-avocado-margarita/\"\u003eadd some avocado \u003c/a\u003eto your recipe!\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" width=\"1333\" height=\"2000\" data-pin-url=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/frozen-margarita-recipe/?tp_image_id=134408\" data-pin-title=\"the best frozen margarita\" src=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/frozen-margaritas-best-1-3.jpg\" alt=\"frozen margarita\" srcset=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/frozen-margaritas-best-1-3.jpg 1333w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/frozen-margaritas-best-1-3-200x300.jpg 200w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/frozen-marga