0w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/frozen-margaritas-best-1-3-730x1095.jpg 730w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/frozen-margaritas-best-1-3-700x1050.jpg 700w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/frozen-margaritas-best-1-3-550x825.jpg 550w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/frozen-margaritas-best-1-3-156x234.jpg 156w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/frozen-margaritas-best-1-3.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003ch2\u003eFrequently Asked Questions\u003c/h2\u003e\u003cdetails id=\"faq-question-1731600666703\"\u003e\u003csummary\u003e\u003ch3\u003eWhat can I use instead of orange liqueur?\u003c/h3\u003e\u003c/summary\u003e \u003cp\u003eWhile it’s popular to use Cointreau or Grand Marnier in place of triple sec in margarita recipes, you can also use fresh orange juice to add an orange flavor and natural sweetness if that’s all you have on hand.\u003c/p\u003e \u003c/details\u003e \u003cdetails id=\"faq-question-1731600909851\"\u003e\u003csummary\u003e\u003ch3\u003eHow do I make a pitcher of frozen margaritas?\u003c/h3\u003e\u003c/summary\u003e \u003cp\u003eTo make a pitcher that serves eight, simply double this recipe and pour into a pitcher to serve in salt-rimmed glasses. You can also store the pitcher in the freezer for a few hours before the party or in between servings to help keep it cold and slushy.\u003c/p\u003e \u003c/details\u003e \u003c/div\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" width=\"1333\" height=\"2000\" data-pin-url=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/frozen-margarita-recipe/?tp_image_id=134409\" data-pin-title=\"the best frozen margarita\" src=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/frozen-margaritas-best-1-4.jpg\" alt=\"frozen margarita\" srcset=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/frozen-margaritas-best-1-4.jpg 1333w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/upload